explicitInput.esqlQuery:
FROM metrics*
| WHERE otelcol_receiver_accepted_metric_points IS NOT NULL
| STATS receiver = VALUES(receiver) BY service.instance.id
| GROK ?instance """(?<target_instance>[^(]*) \(.*\)"""
| WHERE target_instance == service.instance.id
| EVAL receiver = MV_APPEND(receiver, "--ALL--")
| MV_EXPAND receiver
| STATS BY receiver
| SORT receiver
explicitInput.title: metrics_receiver

query.esql:
TS metrics*
| WHERE ?metrics_receiver == "--ALL--" OR (receiver IS NOT NULL AND ?metrics_receiver == receiver)
| WHERE ?metrics_receiver_transport == "--ALL--" OR (transport IS NOT NULL AND ?metrics_receiver_transport == transport)
| KEEP @timestamp, otelcol_receiver_accepted_metric_points, receiver, transport, service.instance.id
| STATS metric_points_rate = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_receiver_accepted_metric_points)) BY service.instance.id
| GROK ?instance """(?<target_instance>[^(]*) \(.*\)"""
| WHERE target_instance == service.instance.id
| KEEP metric_points_rate
